Alabasta's Guardian Angel!

37
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:36,990
Crocodile!

38
00:03:37,070 --> 00:03:37,930
Crocodile!

39
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:40,630
King of the desert! Crocodile!

40
