59
00:06:15,370 --> 00:06:18,730
By the time we got to Nanohana,
it was already...

60
00:06:19,090 --> 00:06:20,920
I see...

61
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:23,560
Either way, it's fine as long
as the citizens are okay.

62
00:06:23,590 --> 00:06:27,300
"King of Alabasta, Nefertari Cobra"

63
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,640
He does a lot for us.

64
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:34,550
There's no mistake.
This ship is heading to Alabasta.

65
00:06:38,650 --> 00:06:40,730
I'll be there soon...

66
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,710
Luffy! Don't lie!

67
00:06:44,550 --> 00:06:46,650
Tell me what you know.

68
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:51,120
Hey, why are you looking away?
Look me in the eyes!

69
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:56,080
Well, seriously... I don't know anything.

70
00:06:56,350 --> 00:06:57,790
Then let me ask you something.

71
00:06:57,790 --> 00:06:59,400
How did enough food for 8 people,

72
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:03,470
which I carefully divided so that
it'd last until we get to Alabasta,

73
00:07:03,470 --> 00:07:05,320
disappear during the night?

74
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:10,350
Stop fighting, it's pointless!
You've got a horrible poker face.

75
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:11,440
Burp...

76
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:17,730
Hey, you have something
around your mouth.

77
00:07:17,730 --> 00:07:20,200
Ah! Shoot! Food crumbs?!

78
00:07:21,730 --> 00:07:24,400
See, it was you!

79
